A 14-year-old girl was on Sunday night, allegedly hypnotized and raped to death by one Ifeanyi Osuji, a 22-year-old suspected internet fraudster, in Agbahara-Nsu community in the Ehime Mbano Local Government Area of Imo State DAILY POST gathered that the victim, identified as Amarachi Iwunze, was invited over by one Ifeanyi Osuji a native of the same community on Saturday. A family source who spoke to our correspondent on condition of anonymity said the victim’s corpse was discovered in the suspect’s room on Sunday by the suspect’s mother. He said “little Amarachi Iwunze from Umuduruewuru, Umuezeala Nsu Autonomous Community in Ehime Mbano LGA of Imo State was raped to death on Sunday, by one Ifeanyi Osuji a suspected Yahoo plus boy/ Ritualist from Agbaghara Nsu Autonomous Community in Ehime Mbano LGA Area of Imo State. According to him, ” The ugly news came late hours of yesterday, when the mother of the suspect unlocked a room and found the dead body of little Amarachi lying lifeless, on raising an alarm, it was discovered that Ifeanyi Osuji is the suspect and the killer. “When Ifeanyi Osuji found out that people are now aware of his ugly act he took to his heels to an unknown destination till this very moment he is wanted. A development which according to him led to a Monday morning protest by the community youths who razed the house of a 22-year-old suspected internet fraudster. Meanwhile, the remains of the victim, stained with semen was found in the suspect’s room in the house which had a gate and fence. When contacted, the Police Public Relations Officer, PPRO in the State, Micheal Abattam, confirmed the incident and said an investigation had commenced.